<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>[الآيات الواردة في <span class="c2">«ترك الصلاة»</span>]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١- إِنَّ الْمُنافِقِينَ يُخادِعُونَ اللَّهَ وَهُوَ خادِعُهُمْ وَإِذا قامُوا إِلَى الصَّلاةِ قامُوا كُسالى يُراؤُنَ النَّاسَ وَلا يَذْكُرُونَ اللَّهَ إِلَّا قَلِيلًا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٤٢)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢- وَما مَنَعَهُمْ أَنْ تُقْبَلَ مِنْهُمْ نَفَقاتُهُمْ إِلَّا أَنَّهُمْ كَفَرُوا بِاللَّهِ وَبِرَسُولِهِ وَلا يَأْتُونَ الصَّلاةَ إِلَّا وَهُمْ كُسالى وَلا يُنْفِقُونَ إِلَّا وَهُمْ كارِهُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣- فَخَلَفَ مِنْ بَعْدِهِمْ خَلْفٌ أَضاعُوا الصَّلاةَ وَاتَّبَعُوا الشَّهَواتِ فَسَوْفَ يَلْقَوْنَ غَيًّا <span class="c2">(٥٩)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٤- كُلُّ نَفْسٍ بِما كَسَبَتْ رَهِينَةٌ <span class="c2">(٣٨)</span> إِلَّا أَصْحابَ الْيَمِينِ <span class="c2">(٣٩)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فِي جَنَّاتٍ يَتَساءَلُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٠)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>عَنِ الْمُجْرِمِينَ <span class="c2">(٤١)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ما سَلَكَكُمْ فِي سَقَرَ <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>قالُوا لَمْ نَكُ مِنَ الْمُصَلِّينَ <span class="c2">(٤٣)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَلَمْ نَكُ نُطْعِمُ الْمِسْكِينَ <span class="c2">(٤٤)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَكُنَّا نَخُوضُ مَعَ الْخائِضِينَ <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَكُنَّا نُكَذِّبُ بِيَوْمِ الدِّينِ <span class="c2">(٤٦)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>حَتَّى أَتانَا الْيَقِينُ <span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٥- فَوَيْلٌ لِلْمُصَلِّينَ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>الَّذِينَ هُمْ عَنْ صَلاتِهِمْ ساهُونَ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>الَّذِينَ هُمْ يُراؤُنَ <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَيَمْنَعُونَ الْماعُونَ <span class="c2">(٧)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
